    "title": "Temperatura crítica para rubidio-87",
    "enunciado": "Calcula T_c para m = 1.443 × 10^{-25} kg, n = 10^{20} m^{-3}, ζ(3/2) = 2.612, k_B = 1.38 × 10^{-23} J/K, ℏ = 1.055 × 10^{-34} J·s.",
    "solution": {
      "steps": [
        "Datos: m = 1.443 × 10^{-25} kg, n = 10^{20} m^{-3}, ζ(3/2) = 2.612, k_B = 1.38 × 10^{-23} J/K, ℏ = 1.055 × 10^{-34} J·s",
        "T_c = (2πℏ² / m k_B) × (n/ζ(3/2))^{2/3}",
        "T_c = (2π×(1.055×10^{-34})^2/(1.443×10^{-25}×1.38×10^{-23}))×(10^{20}/2.612)^{2/3}",
        "Resultado: T_c ≈ 2×10^{-7} K"
      ],
      "result": "2×10^{-7} K"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "bec-ejercicio-03",
